modName: Rose Tyler-Torn from time and space
summary: A save game made of Rose Tyler from Doctor Who
descriptionHtml:
Rose Tyler Torn from Time

This is my attempt to capture the beauty of Miss Billie Piper; the actress of Rose Tyler from Doctor Who.
This is a save game file that begins in alternate start version 2.41.
PLEASE NOTE…. Pictures uploaded are at Solitude docks in the light, because the lighting in the alternate start is not great for pictures.
You will start off in the Alternate start before speaking to Mara so YOU can pick your beginning.
This save REQUIRES the Following

Alternate Start by Arthmoor Version 2.41
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/9557
RaceMenu by Expired Version 2.91
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?
Brows by Hvergelmir Normal Resolution Version 2
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/
ApachiiSkyHair by Apachii HairFemale Version 1.4 the Standalone female hairs
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/
Also note Sky UI and Skse are required for the above mods
IMPORTANT OTHER MODS ARE INSTALLED WITH THIS SAVE FILE SO A MISSING DATA MESSAGE WILL APPEAR JUST DISREGARD IT AS THEY ARE NOT NECESSARY FOR ROSE’S APPERANCE.
Note if you want Rose as a companion I suggest the mod Familiar Faces by Verteiron
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54509/
P.S. If you any suggestion by all means comment away.
author: ALittleLostElf
